nodes.text: Daphry was a member of the Lok Revenants in 32 BBY.

Daphry was in a Revenant Speeder patrolling Sector 3 on Lok the night after the captain Nym brought in stolen Trade Federation cargo. Daphry patrolled under the call sign 21-R5. Just as he was ordered to move to another sector, Daphry was killed when his speeder crested a hill, and crashed into an Armored Assault Tank.
